TY  - JOUR
T1  - Split or Steal? Cooperative Behavior When the Stakes Are Large
AU  - van den Assem, Martijn J.
AU  - van Dolder, Dennie
AU  - Thaler, Richard H.
Y1  - 2011/10/07
